                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">coming from a special server *Legends* I see a huge influx/outflux of items/platinum.
<br />

<br />
Typically the way it works, is someone with a hugely bad rep, buys items up cheap on their home server (or steals from their friends/guild), then moves to legends to unload them.
<br />

<br />
On the flip side of the coin, people buy platinum on legends (unlimited supply) and take advantage of the high density of items (although we don't have alot of vendors); they stock up, then move home, or go to a different server with a free name change and their ill gotten gains.
<br />

<br />
The way this tends to work is our high end items are a bit more reasonable because they come from all servers and our own, while our low end tradeskill items are not typically farmed, are VERY expensive, and sell VERY fast on stormhammer.
<br />

<br />
I personally would support any action to destroy the ebay/PA economy including a complete wipe of EVERY bank account in the game.  (I only have about 700k in plat and maybe a million plat or so in droppables)</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=259328" target="_blank" class="postlink"><img src="http://www.sinann.net/Nanyea.jpg" border="0" /></a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
