1) The ubber character for whom plat means nothing really has no voice here.  It's like Trump saying the cost of housing is cheap.  He's smoking dope, so are they.  If your going to comment on something that effects the 90 percentile, you need to be <span style="text-decoration: underline">part </span>of the 90 percentile.
<br />

<br />
2) It's a known fact that Yantis/IGE basically have hosed the game economies, and ruined the game play value of thousands of people by allowing eBay'd diablo 2 fan boys to spring into game at the high level.  And people still give them money.  SoE for thier part have abandoned the issue.  Most likely in light of the fact that recent court events have shown the EULA to have non-enforceble sections with regards to virtual property.
<br />

<br />
